title: Safety 1st Easy Install 28" High Walk Thru Gate, Fits Between 29" and 38"
description: Now that baby is on the move, the Safety 1st Easy Install Walk-Through Gate makes it simple to create child friendly areas within your home. For use between rooms, a walk-through gate makes it easy to get around the house, with no need to reinstall it each time you pass by. Pressure-mounted gates provide flexibility in usage around the home.  Wall cups stay installed to the wall while the gate can easily be removed for periods of non-use. This pressure mounted baby gate is 28 inches high and can be adjusted from 29 to 38 inches for doorways of varying widths throughout your home.  The Safety 1st Easy Install Walk-Through Gate isn’t just for kids either. It comes in handy when you’re trying to keep pets out of certain rooms as well.
